metadata.name: Chaos and Delight
metadata.description:
The character that reclines into chaos and seeks a moment of rest, reminds us of the constancy in which our bodies are asleep, but our streams of thoughts never give themselves a second's rest.
Fighting against it sometimes becomes almost impossible.

Sorriso and logbook merge their research, seeking a singular image, seeking a new organization to their thoughts and understandings as a form of shelter and welcome.
